‘‘‘Imamatthaṃ, bhante, brahmā sanaṅkumāro devānaṃ tāvatiṃsānaṃ abhāsi, imamatthaṃ vessavaṇo mahārājā brahmuno sanaṅkumārassa devānaṃ tāvatiṃsānaṃ bhāsato  sammukhā sutaṃsutvā 
Note { id=32, line='295', referenceLine='68', original='sutvā (sī. pī.)', type='auto', previous=' sammukhā sutaṃ '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='sutaṃ'}
	Alternative{lang='sī. pī.', text='sutvā'}}
sammukhā paṭiggahitaṃ sayaṃ parisāyaṃ ārocesi’’.

Imamatthaṃ janavasabho yakkho vessavaṇassa mahārājassa sayaṃ parisāyaṃ bhāsato sammukhā sutaṃ sammukhā paṭiggahitaṃpaṭiggahetvā 
Note { id=33, line='304', referenceLine='69', original='paṭiggahetvā (sī. pī.)', type='auto', previous='Imamatthaṃ janavasabho yakkho vessavaṇassa mahārājassa sayaṃ parisāyaṃ bhāsato sammukhā sutaṃ sammukhā paṭiggahitaṃ '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='paṭiggahitaṃ'}
	Alternative{lang='sī. pī.', text='paṭiggahetvā'}}
bhagavato ārocesi. Imamatthaṃ bhagavā janavasabhassa yakkhassa sammukhā sutvā sammukhā paṭiggahetvā sāmañca abhiññāya āyasmato ānandassa ārocesi, imamatthamāyasmā ānando bhagavato sammukhā sutvā sammukhā paṭiggahetvā ārocesi bhikkhūnaṃ bhikkhunīnaṃ upāsakānaṃ upāsikānaṃ. Tayidaṃ brahmacariyaṃ iddhañceva phītañca vitthārikaṃ bāhujaññaṃ puthubhūtaṃ yāva devamanussehi suppakāsitanti.
